data.description: Beautiful open floor plan, 3 bed 2 bath home with heated pool and spa. Spacious primary bedroom has a large bathroom with garden tub, separate shower, dual sinks, walk in closet, French doors to the pool area. Split bedrooms, Kitchen / family room combo, dinette overlooking the pool area. Dining, living area combo. Close to US 27 and Interstate 4 for easy access to Tampa and Orlando. Loma Del Sol is a residential community, no short-term rentals allowed. Roof and pool heater 2017, AC 2019 and new windows in 2020. Windows have a Kevlar protection system.
